### Alle Spots abrufen
GET http://localhost:8081/api/spots
Accept: application/json

### Eigenen Spots abrufen
GET http://localhost:8081/api/spots/mine?user=Moritz
Accept: application/json

### Neuen Spot erstellen
POST http://localhost:8081/api/spots
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Seerhein Park",
  "description": "Schöner Park am Fluss",
  "createdBy": "Moritz",
  "location": "Seerhein"
}

### Spot aktualisieren
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/spots/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hafen Konstanz Updated",
  "description": "Schöner Hafen mit Restaurants und Cafés",
  "createdBy": "Moritz",
  "location": "Hafenstraße 1"
}

### Spot löschen
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/spots/1
